<div id="comments" class="comment-list hot show">
        <ul>
                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="934696255">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-934696255" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-934696255" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="934696255">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/69011211/">不神秘</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-07-06</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">很好的入门书，宋以前均极佳。尤其胡阿祥纵论魏晋南北朝，非常开阔。上古史两篇也好。相比之下，明清史部分则逊色很多。收入论文以中国学者，尤其是老一辈学人的为主。真是感慨他们的气势磅礴，高屋建瓴。当然，不是每个人都这样。其实可以考虑收入一些文革后学者的论文。后悔自己没有早点看到此书，否则学中古史也不一定...</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="725266792">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-725266792" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-725266792" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="725266792">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/44670712/">复诵</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-09-11</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">个人感觉这套相比于北大那套论文选集，选取的研究论文更有普遍性和可读性。也更有代表性。北大那套的学术性更强。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
